                                    </div>
</td>
<td class="px-4 py-1 text-right text-on-surface">-$412.50</td>
</tr>
<!-- Cleared Row -->
<tr class="border-b border-border-low-contrast/30 hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors bg-surface-container-lowest/10">
